post.body: I'm reading it for the 2nd time in prep for my New Years Revolution series! Incredibly challenging!
sorry for the memories...

Good Morning life...
I was reading a lil Shane Claiborne but this new show Leverage stole my attention. Decent, but won't take the place of The Mentalist.
Its been a slow day of twittering...my internet was messed on my blueberry.
Bout to get it on at BWW! Yes siree!

Def not a barista yet...this thing is complicated!

Read Matthew 7:21-23 in The Message...serious cup check...let's not fall into that!
Just got a $300 espresso machine for $85...I'm pumped. Macchiatos on the house!!!
Concord Mills still has Christmas Music playing...they should be shut down!
Thought it was an 11 hour trip home but the Garmin tells me 9...that is euangelion!
Walking into NewSpring! Pretty pumped about this!!
Wish we had a few more days in the Carolina's! Can't wait to get back to Dela-who tho and get Fuel and Traffic rollin'!!!
Wow, that just happened! I slept for 11 hours!!!!
